<P>31. Toronto Urban Forestry issued permit no. S-8662839 on April 19, 2018 to allow the Applicants to have the Tree removed (the &ldquo;Tree Destruction Permit&rdquo;) citing the renovation plan could not be reasonably completed if the Tree were not removed. The Respondents were copied by Toronto Urban Forestry on the notice issuing the Tree Destruction Permit.
