<BLOCK3><TI><EM>Approval of City of Toronto Building Department</EM></TI>
<P>33. On May 10, 2018, Spragge &amp; Company applied to the City of Toronto on behalf of the Applicants for building permits for the proposed renovation at[location omitted]
