<P>34. On June 20, 2018 the City of Toronto issued to the Applicants two building permits for the addition and renovation being: building permit 18 157345 PLB 00 PS; and, building permit 18 157345 BLD 00 SR (collectively, the &ldquo;Building Permits&rdquo;). Both Building Permits are based upon the destruction of the Tree to complete the addition and renovation.
