<P>35. The Tree is preventing the Applicants from building the addition and renovation they require for their family. The Tree is one of five mature and very large trees on [location omitted], all of which provide abundant shade and canopy to both [location omitted] and [location omitted]. Under the Tree Destruction Permit, the Applicants are obligated to plant two replacement trees, which is a small part of a landscaping plan involving the planting of numerous additional plants, shrubs, and trees once the renovation is completed.
